---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Redis Cluster Hashing & Failover" 
  description="Interactive visualization of Redis Cluster hash slots, CRC16 routing, topology, MOVED/ASK redirections, and automatic failover"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: "Home", href: "/" }, 
    { label: "Redis", href: "/redis/" },
    { label: "Cluster Hashing", href: "/redis/cluster-hashing/" }
  ]}
>
  <div class="viz-container">
    <header class="viz-header">
      <h1>🔴 Cluster Hashing & Failover</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How Redis Distributes Keys Across Nodes and Recovers From Failures</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="overview-section">
      <div class="overview-card">
        <p>
          Redis Cluster splits all data into <strong>16,384 hash slots</strong>. Every key is mapped to a slot
          via <em>CRC16(key) mod 16384</em>. Each master node owns a range of slots, and every node knows the 
          full slot→node mapping via a <strong>gossip protocol</strong> over the cluster bus. If a client hits 
          the wrong node, it gets a <em>MOVED</em> or <em>ASK</em> redirection. When a master dies, its replica 
          automatically promotes itself and takes over.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key → Slot Calculator -->
    <section class="flow-section">
      <h2>🔑 Key → Slot Calculator</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Type a key to see which hash slot it maps to and which node owns it</p>

      <div class="calculator-container">
        <div class="calc-input-row">
          <input type="text" id="keyInput" placeholder="Type a Redis key (e.g. user:1001)" class="key-input" autocomplete="off">
          <button id="calcBtn" class="action-btn primary-btn">Calculate</button>
        </div>
        <div class="calc-result" id="calcResult"></div>
        <div class="calc-formula" id="calcFormula"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Hash Slot Grid -->
    <section class="flow-section">
      <h2>📊 Hash Slot Distribution</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">All 16,384 slots colored by owning node. Adjust cluster size to see redistribution.</p>

      <div class="flow-controls">
        <div class="slider-group">
          <label>Masters: <strong id="masterCountLabel">3</strong></label>
          <input type="range" id="masterSlider" min="3" max="6" value="3" class="slot-slider">
        </div>
        <button id="redistributeBtn" class="action-btn primary-btn">🔄 Redistribute</button>
      </div>

      <div class="node-legend" id="nodeLegend"></div>
      <div class="slot-grid-wrapper">
        <canvas id="slotCanvas" width="820" height="200"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="slot-hover-info" id="slotHoverInfo">Hover over the grid to inspect slots</div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cluster Topology -->
    <section class="flow-section">
      <h2>🌐 Cluster Topology</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Click a node to see its slot range, replicas, and connections. Every node knows the full mapping.</p>

      <div class="topology-container">
        <canvas id="topoCanvas" width="820" height="450"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="topo-info-panel" id="topoInfoPanel">
        <p class="topo-hint">Click a node above to inspect it</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MOVED / ASK Redirections -->
    <section class="explain-section">
      <div class="explain-grid">
        <div class="explain-card">
          <h3>↩️ MOVED Redirection</h3>
          <p>
            Client sends <code>GET user:42</code> to Node A, but the slot belongs to Node C. 
            Node A responds: <code>MOVED 12345 node-c:6379</code>. The client <strong>updates its slot map</strong> 
            and retries on Node C. Permanent — the slot has moved.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="explain-card">
          <h3>🔀 ASK Redirection</h3>
          <p>
            During a slot <strong>migration</strong>, some keys may have moved to the target node but the slot 
            isn't fully transferred yet. The source responds <code>ASK 12345 node-c:6379</code>. 
            The client sends <code>ASKING</code> then retries — but does <em>not</em> update its map. Temporary.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Failover Section -->
    <section class="flow-section">
      <h2>💥 Failover Simulation</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Kill a master node and watch the cluster detect the failure and promote a replica</p>

      <div class="flow-controls">
        <button id="killNodeBtn" class="action-btn kill-btn">💀 Kill Master</button>
        <button id="stepFailoverBtn" class="action-btn step-btn" disabled>⏭ Next Step</button>
        <button id="autoFailoverBtn" class="action-btn auto-btn" disabled>⚡ Auto-Play</button>
        <button id="resetFailoverBtn" class="action-btn reset-btn">🔄 Reset</button>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-status" id="failoverStatus">
        <span class="status-badge idle" id="failoverBadge">Ready</span>
        <span class="status-text" id="failoverStatusText">Click "Kill Master" to begin the failover simulation</span>
      </div>

      <div class="failover-viz">
        <canvas id="failoverCanvas" width="820" height="320"></canvas>
      </div>

      <div class="failover-timeline" id="failoverTimeline"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Failover Explainer -->
    <section class="explain-section">
      <div class="explain-card highlight-card">
        <h3>💡 How Failover Works</h3>
        <p>
          Every node pings every other node every <strong>1 second</strong> via the cluster bus (port + 10000). 
          If a node doesn't respond within <code>cluster-node-timeout</code>, the pinging node marks it 
          <em>PFAIL</em> (subjective failure). When a <strong>majority of masters</strong> agree a node is 
          PFAIL, it becomes <em>FAIL</em> (objective failure). The dead master's replica then starts an 
          <strong>election</strong>: it increments the epoch, asks masters to vote, and upon winning promotes 
          itself — taking over the master's slots. The whole process typically completes in 
          <strong>1–2 × node-timeout</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Slot Migration -->
    <section class="flow-section">
      <h2>📦 Slot Migration</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Watch keys migrate from one node to another, slot by slot</p>

      <div class="flow-controls">
        <button id="startMigrateBtn" class="action-btn primary-btn">▶ Start Migration</button>
        <button id="resetMigrateBtn" class="action-btn reset-btn">🔄 Reset</button>
      </div>

      <div class="migration-viz" id="migrationViz">
        <div class="migrate-node migrate-source">
          <h4>Source: Node A</h4>
          <div class="migrate-slots" id="migrateSource"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="migrate-arrow" id="migrateArrow">
          <div class="migrate-arrow-line"></div>
          <div class="migrate-key-flying" id="flyingKey" style="display:none;">📦</div>
        </div>
        <div class="migrate-node migrate-target">
          <h4>Target: Node B</h4>
          <div class="migrate-slots" id="migrateTarget"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="migrate-log" id="migrateLog"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Network Partition -->
    <section class="flow-section">
      <h2>🔌 Network Partition</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">What happens when nodes can't talk to each other?</p>

      <div class="flow-controls">
        <button id="partitionBtn" class="action-btn kill-btn">⚡ Create Partition</button>
        <button id="healBtn" class="action-btn primary-btn" disabled>🩹 Heal Partition</button>
        <button id="resetPartitionBtn" class="action-btn reset-btn">🔄 Reset</button>
      </div>

      <div class="partition-viz">
        <canvas id="partitionCanvas" width="820" height="300"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="partition-log" id="partitionLog"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Manual Failover -->
    <section class="explain-section">
      <div class="explain-grid">
        <div class="explain-card">
          <h3>🔧 Manual Failover</h3>
          <p>
            Run <code>CLUSTER FAILOVER</code> on a replica to gracefully promote it. 
            The replica tells its master to <strong>stop accepting writes</strong>, waits for replication 
            offset to match, then swaps roles. <strong>Zero data loss</strong> — unlike automatic failover 
            where the last few writes may be lost.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="explain-card">
          <h3>📐 Cluster Bus Protocol</h3>
          <p>
            Nodes communicate via a binary protocol on <strong>port + 10000</strong>. 
            Each message carries the sender's view of the cluster: node IDs, slot ownership, 
            flags (PFAIL/FAIL), and epoch numbers. This is how the <em>gossip protocol</em> 
            propagates configuration changes — eventually consistent, but fast.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="viz-footer">
      <p>Based on <a href="https://redis.io/docs/management/scaling/" target="_blank">Redis Cluster Documentation</a> and <a href="https://redis.io/docs/reference/cluster-spec/" target="_blank">Redis Cluster Specification</a></p>
    </footer>

    <div class="share-buttons">
      <span>Share this visualization:</span>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Interactive%20visualization%20of%20Redis%20Cluster%20hashing%20and%20failover&url=https://systeminternals.dev/redis/cluster-hashing/" target="_blank" class="share-btn">𝕏 Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https://systeminternals.dev/redis/cluster-hashing/" target="_blank" class="share-btn">in LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/submitlink?u=https://systeminternals.dev/redis/cluster-hashing/&t=Interactive%20Redis%20Cluster%20Hashing%20%26%20Failover%20Visualizer" target="_blank" class="share-btn">🟧 Hacker News</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .viz-container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .viz-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .viz-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f97316, #eab308);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-desc {
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* Overview */
  .overview-section {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .overview-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1), rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05));
    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .overview-card strong { color: #fff; }
  .overview-card em { color: #f97316; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; }
  .overview-card a { color: #60a5fa; }

  /* Action Buttons */
  .action-btn {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .action-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .primary-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626);
    color: white;
  }

  .primary-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
  }

  .step-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #3b82f6);
    color: white;
  }

  .auto-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #ea580c);
    color: white;
  }

  .kill-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #b91c1c);
    color: white;
  }

  .kill-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.5);
  }

  .reset-btn {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: #aaa;
  }

  .reset-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; }

  /* Flow Section */
  .flow-section {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .flow-controls {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .flow-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .status-badge {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .status-badge.idle { background: rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.3); color: #9ca3af; }
  .status-badge.detecting { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2); color: #fbbf24; }
  .status-badge.electing { background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2); color: #f97316; }
  .status-badge.promoting { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2); color: #22c55e; }
  .status-badge.done { background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.2); color: #60a5fa; }
  .status-badge.failed { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); color: #ef4444; }

  .status-text {
    color: #aaa;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Calculator */
  .calculator-container {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .calc-input-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .key-input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .key-input:focus {
    border-color: #ef4444;
  }

  .key-input::placeholder {
    color: #555;
  }

  .calc-result {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    min-height: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .calc-formula {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
    margin-top: 8px;
    min-height: 24px;
  }

  /* Slot Grid */
  .slider-group {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .slider-group label {
    color: #ccc;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .slider-group strong {
    color: #ef4444;
  }

  .slot-slider {
    width: 160px;
    height: 8px;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .slot-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ef4444;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .node-legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  :global(.legend-item) {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  :global(.legend-swatch) {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .slot-grid-wrapper {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .slot-hover-info {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8px;
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
  }

  /* Topology */
  .topology-container {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .topo-info-panel {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    min-height: 80px;
  }

  .topo-hint {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Failover */
  .failover-viz {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .failover-timeline {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    min-height: 60px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  :global(.failover-step) {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    animation: eventAppear 0.4s ease-out;
  }

  :global(.failover-step.detect-step) { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fde68a; border-left: 3px solid #fbbf24; }
  :global(.failover-step.fail-step) { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15); color: #fca5a5; border-left: 3px solid #ef4444; }
  :global(.failover-step.elect-step) { background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1); color: #fed7aa; border-left: 3px solid #f97316; }
  :global(.failover-step.promote-step) { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15); color: #86efac; border-left: 3px solid #22c55e; }

  @keyframes eventAppear {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* Migration */
  .migration-viz {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .migrate-node {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .migrate-node h4 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .migrate-source { border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3); }
  .migrate-source h4 { color: #60a5fa; }
  .migrate-target { border-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3); }
  .migrate-target h4 { color: #4ade80; }

  .migrate-slots {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    min-height: 40px;
  }

  :global(.migrate-slot) {
    width: 42px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  :global(.migrate-slot.source-slot) {
    background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.4);
    color: #93c5fd;
  }

  :global(.migrate-slot.target-slot) {
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
    color: #86efac;
    animation: slotAppear 0.4s ease-out;
  }

  :global(.migrate-slot.migrating) {
    background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
    border-color: #fbbf24;
    color: #fde68a;
    animation: pulse 0.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes slotAppear {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
  }

  .migrate-arrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    position: relative;
    width: 80px;
  }

  .migrate-arrow-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .migrate-arrow-line::after {
    content: '▶';
    position: absolute;
    right: -14px;
    top: -8px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .migrate-key-flying {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    animation: flyAcross 0.8s ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes flyAcross {
    0% { transform: translateX(-30px); opacity: 0; }
    30% { opacity: 1; }
    70% { opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: translateX(30px); opacity: 0; }
  }

  .migrate-log {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    min-height: 60px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    max-height: 200px;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  :global(.migrate-log-entry) {
    padding: 4px 0;
    color: #aaa;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    animation: eventAppear 0.3s ease-out;
  }

  :global(.migrate-log-entry .cmd) { color: #4ade80; }
  :global(.migrate-log-entry .info) { color: #60a5fa; }

  /* Partition */
  .partition-viz {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .partition-log {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    min-height: 60px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    max-height: 200px;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  :global(.partition-entry) {
    padding: 6px 10px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    animation: eventAppear 0.3s ease-out;
  }

  :global(.partition-entry.warning) { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fde68a; border-left: 3px solid #fbbf24; }
  :global(.partition-entry.error) { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); color: #fca5a5; border-left: 3px solid #ef4444; }
  :global(.partition-entry.success) { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); color: #86efac; border-left: 3px solid #22c55e; }
  :global(.partition-entry.info-entry) { background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1); color: #93c5fd; border-left: 3px solid #60a5fa; }

